---
title: Honey-Sesame Double Beef Steak Bowl with Asian-Style Slaw & Rapid Butter Rice
description: Inject your night with a burst of flavour by combining sesame seed-topped beef with buttery basmati rice. Top this baby off with
an Asian-style slaw and a dollop of soy mayo for a dish that’ll have you salivating long before you plate up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-sesame-double-beef-steak-bowl-3a422fb0.jpg
